com.tallygo.tallygoandroid.endpoint.search

Class TGSuggestion

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.tallygo.tallygoandroid.sdk.TGBaseObject
      • com.tallygo.tallygoandroid.endpoint.search.TGSuggestion

  • public class TGSuggestion
extends TGBaseObject
    This is an autocomplete suggestion. To get full info including location, make a call to TallyGo.getTGSearch() and include the suggestionKey value from the suggestion.
